ing: 1 (1 ounce) package instant sugar-free pistachio pudding mix
1 (8 ounce) can unsweetened crushed pineapple, undrained
des: "Anyone who likes the combination of pistachio pudding and pineapple will love this trimmed down, yet still creamy version."
ins: In a large bowl, combine pistachio pudding mix, plain yogurt, vanilla yogurt and crushed pineapple. Mix until smooth. Fold in whipped topping. Cover, and refrigerate until chilled.
